    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Start fresh in the charming town of <strong>Hearthstone Bay!</strong> Inherit your grandmother’s cafe, a warm and welcoming hub for locals, and step into a world where community bonds are just as essential as crafting the perfect cup of coffee. As you connect with the townsfolk, you’ll uncover secrets, restore the cafe, and work toward revitalizing the entire town.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Design and Run Your Dream Cafe</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> </strong>Create a cozy space that reflects your style and the spirit of Hearthstone Bay. Decorate your cafe with warm decor and unique furniture, making it feel like home for both you and your customers.<br> <br>  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194420/extras/9998dd20c0e2e9e9391de08645e6f27d.poster.avif?t=1731699498\" width=616 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194420/extras/9998dd20c0e2e9e9391de08645e6f27d.webm?t=1731699498\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194420/extras/9998dd20c0e2e9e9391de08645e6f27d.mp4?t=1731699498\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Hone Your Barista Skills</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong> </strong>Master the art of coffee with a growing list of recipes. Start with the basics, discover community favorites, and experiment to create new flavors as you become the town’s favorite barista.  <br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194420/extras/fdf5f3701934ba93dce35f192e8f3d55.poster.avif?t=1731699498\" width=616 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194420/extras/fdf5f3701934ba93dce35f192e8f3d55.webm?t=1731699498\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194420/extras/fdf5f3701934ba93dce35f192e8f3d55.mp4?t=1731699498\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Build Trust and Relationships</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> </strong>Each resident has a unique story, dreams, and struggles. Befriend the townsfolk, earn their trust, and uncover their personal histories. <strong>Your reliability status affects product prices, customer loyalty, and quest opportunities, making every interaction meaningful.</strong><br> <br>  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194420/extras/21fac0e05d53d12d58ce546f50fd7507.poster.avif?t=1731699498\" width=616 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194420/extras/21fac0e05d53d12d58ce546f50fd7507.webm?t=1731699498\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194420/extras/21fac0e05d53d12d58ce546f50fd7507.mp4?t=1731699498\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Dynamic Market Prices</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >!!! Your <strong>Reliability Status</strong> influences the deals you get from suppliers. Maintain high reliability to secure the best prices, or face higher costs if trust falters, adding a strategic layer to managing your cafe’s finances :). !!! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194420/extras/24771ff57e89ceb8ac7a0ec931cec717.poster.avif?t=1731699498\" width=616 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194420/extras/24771ff57e89ceb8ac7a0ec931cec717.webm?t=1731699498\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194420/extras/24771ff57e89ceb8ac7a0ec931cec717.mp4?t=1731699498\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Balance Prices and Manage Customer Satisfaction</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> </strong>Set prices that keep customers happy and sustain your cafe’s growth. Your reliability status plays a role in customer loyalty and supplier prices, so each decision matters.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194420/extras/701ab3dd4adaa13635ef745b2f73d030.poster.avif?t=1731699498\" width=616 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194420/extras/701ab3dd4adaa13635ef745b2f73d030.webm?t=1731699498\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194420/extras/701ab3dd4adaa13635ef745b2f73d030.mp4?t=1731699498\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Hire and Build a Loyal Team</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> </strong>As your cafe grows, hire baristas and waitstaff to support your business. Each team member brings unique skills, so choose carefully to create an efficient, inviting atmosphere for customers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194420/extras/03242742b0b383fd1cef64e3e7fb619a.poster.avif?t=1731699498\" width=616 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194420/extras/03242742b0b383fd1cef64e3e7fb619a.webm?t=1731699498\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194420/extras/03242742b0b383fd1cef64e3e7fb619a.mp4?t=1731699498\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Join Festivals and Community Events </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Participate in local festivals and challenges that strengthen your bond with the town. From barista competitions to fishing festivals, there’s always something to celebrate and a new way to connect with the community.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194420/extras/8bb95bc0e4eff0b40621b91440457077.poster.avif?t=1731699498\" width=616 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194420/extras/8bb95bc0e4eff0b40621b91440457077.webm?t=1731699498\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194420/extras/8bb95bc0e4eff0b40621b91440457077.mp4?t=1731699498\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Don't forget to:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194420/extras/9d9b37be1384de8495408ed26bbe0576.poster.avif?t=1731699498\" width=736 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194420/extras/9d9b37be1384de8495408ed26bbe0576.webm?t=1731699498\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194420/extras/9d9b37be1384de8495408ed26bbe0576.mp4?t=1731699498\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194420/extras/0230e5e225901733f81cbfaa5514b801.avif?t=1731699498\" width=616 height=200 /></span></p>",
